ssion from Cape Canaveral on April 28, 2025. Photo: ULA\\n\\nUnited Launch Alliance (ULA) launched the first full-scale mission for Amazon\\u2019s Project Kuiper constellation on Monday evening, starting the deployment phase of Amazon\\u2019s competitor to Starlink and OneWeb.", "score": 0.71948266, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://currentaffairs.adda247.com/amazon-launched-satellite-for-project-kuiper-broadband-internet", "title": "Amazon Launched Satellite for Project Kuiper Broadband Internet", "content": "### Why in News?\\n\\nOn April 28, 2025, Amazon successfully launched the first 27 satellites of its Project Kuiper broadband internet constellation from Cape Canaveral, Florida, marking the company\\u2019s official entry into the satellite internet race against SpaceX\\u2019s Starlink.\\n\\n### Project Kuiper Launch Details", "score": 0.6994397, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://spaceinsider.tech/2025/04/29/amazon-begins-full-deployment-of-kuiper-internet-satellites-with-ula-launch", "title": "Amazon Begins Full Deployment of Kuiper Internet Satellites with ULA Launch", "content": "Vulcan rocket, aimed at increasing cadence for both commercial and government missions. A United Launch Alliance Atlas V rocket lifted off from Cape Canaveral on April 28, marking the start of full-scale deployment for Amazon\\u2019s Project Kuiper, a satellite network designed to deliver broadband internet service across the globe. \\u201cThis launch is an incredible milestone in Amazon\\u2019s ambitious initiative to provide fast, reliable broadband service to unserved and underserved communities around the", "score": 0.64478505, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.telecomstechnews.com/news/ula-begins-deploying-amazon-project-kuiper-satellites", "title": "ULA begins deploying Amazon Project Kuiper satellites", "content": "Cape Canaveral to support the capacity for future Project Kuiper missions in a manner that will ultimately benefit both our commercial and gove